Package edu.kit.kastel.mcse.ardoco.core.common.util

Class DataRepositoryHelper

java.lang.Object
edu.kit.kastel.mcse.ardoco.core.common.util.DataRepositoryHelper
public final class DataRepositoryHelper extends Object
This class helps to access DataRepositories. It provides methods to access the different PipelineStepData that is stored within the repository that are used within ArDoCo.
